         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-07/1211255879_16270935481761n_1.jpg?NQueouVPi02Jn9E3FfsDTkajNWBN8zcU&itok=a01ERoAQ" alt data-caption="中国选手杨倩以251.8环的成绩，在刚刚结束的东京奥运女子10米气步枪决赛中拿下中国首面金牌。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-07/1211255879_16270935481761n_1.jpg?NQueouVPi02Jn9E3FfsDTkajNWBN8zcU&itok=a01ERoAQ" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>中国选手杨倩以251.8环的成绩，在刚刚结束的东京奥运女子10米气步枪决赛中拿下中国首面金牌。（新华社）</p></figcaption>
