</figcaption>
  
            

<p>命运多舛的2020东京奥林匹克运动会今天终于登场。虽然现场观众不多，但今天傍晚在东京奥林匹克体育场举行的开幕式节目丰富多彩。</p>
      

<figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs1r14bsab13xw7d7ob.jpg?jJb7vqbL_7kL.HRZqUMg2LXzafIfnGoQ&itok=MEoE72yN" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>开幕式上，璀璨的烟火点亮了东京奥运体育场的上空。（法新社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs1r14vk2b4wpn0ihk.jpg?jhpOM4nXeUsftVdTuksqtHy8CeZmQOTq&itok=KKLNrWwG" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>在东京奥运会开幕式上，烟花照亮了奥林匹克体育场上空。（法新社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs1rhyx4g91ra8lghc.jpg?xLJKx904MKH7YrXyXGQEq5GwFkOiIjc3&itok=IOviGEbI" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>今晚在东京奥运会开幕式上的舞蹈表演。（路透社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs1y03re9l1lctp77ob.jpg?nc.cqPHWgoJTe_vCZ2CBX52E5XSnnmvH&itok=S8JxU-OJ" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
